description: Jordan is a bartender at a club that our team frequents.We have had our eye on him for a long time, and when he finally decided to give a shot to becoming a Next Door Male, we knew we were in for a treat. Sure enough, once Jordan took off his shirt, we knew we had a winner. We would've never known it, but he's quite the tease, and by the time he had all of his clothes off, our staff was drooling. We think you will be too.Enjoy Jordan in three scenes. Relaxing in the living room, taking a shower, and then finally in bed.
title: Jordan
